.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-CHANNEL-OPEN-HISTORY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-channel-open-history \- list all channels ever opened
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-channel-open-history
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns all channels (including closed) from
.BR listpeerchannels .
Default limit is 50.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, peer_id, state, funding_txid, total_msat}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-history (1)
